    <section class="section" id="faqs" aria-labelledby="faq-title"><div class="faq-layout shell"><div class="faq-intro reveal"><div class="section-kicker">Location questions</div><h2 id="faq-title">House cleaning area questions.</h2><p>Coverage and availability can vary by suburb, service and date.</p></div><div class="faq-list reveal"><article class="faq-item is-open"><h3><button type="button" class="faq-question" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="areaFaq1" id="areaQuestion1">Do you clean homes outside the listed suburbs?<span class="faq-question__icon"></span></button></h3><div class="faq-answer" id="areaFaq1" role="region" aria-labelledby="areaQuestion1"><div><p>Sometimes we can help just outside a listed boundary when an existing route allows it. Contact us with the address and preferred date so we can check.</p></div></div></article><article class="faq-item"><h3><button type="button" class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="areaFaq2" id="areaQuestion2">Do you service all of greater Melbourne?<span class="faq-question__icon"></span></button></h3><div class="faq-answer" id="areaFaq2" role="region" aria-labelledby="areaQuestion2"><div><p>No. We keep a focused service area so travel remains manageable and scheduling stays reliable.</p></div></div></article><article class="faq-item"><h3><button type="button" class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="areaFaq3" id="areaQuestion3">Does being listed guarantee availability?<span class="faq-question__icon"></span></button></h3><div class="faq-answer" id="areaFaq3" role="region" aria-labelledby="areaQuestion3"><div><p>No. A listed suburb means we service that area, but availability still depends on the date, service type and current route capacity.</p></div></div></article><article class="faq-item"><h3><button type="button" class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="areaFaq4" id="areaQuestion4">Is parking required?<span class="faq-question__icon"></span></button></h3><div class="faq-answer" id="areaFaq4" role="region" aria-labelledby="areaQuestion4"><div><p>Please tell us about permits, visitor bays or paid parking before the booking. Easy access helps the cleaner arrive and begin on time.</p></div></div></article><article class="faq-item"><h3><button type="button" class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="areaFaq5" id="areaQuestion5">Can I book recurring cleaning in my suburb?<span class="faq-question__icon"></span></button></h3><div class="faq-answer" id="areaFaq5" role="region" aria-labelledby="areaQuestion5"><div><p>Recurring bookings depend on an ongoing route and suitable cleaner availability. Enter your location during booking to see the best current options.</p></div></div></article></div></div></section>
    <section class="final-cta"><div class="final-cta__panel">__ASTRO_IMAGE_3__<div class="final-cta__inner shell"><div class="final-cta__content reveal"><span class="eyebrow">Found your suburb?</span><h2>Now let us take care of the home.</h2><p>Choose your service, see your estimate, and book online in minutes. We cover 70+ Melbourne suburbs with vetted, insured professionals.</p><a class="button button--primary" href="/pricing#calculator">Build my clean <span class="button__icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path d="M4 10h11M11 6l4 4-4 4"></path></svg></span></a></div></div></div></section>
